<%- include("./partials/header") %>
		
	<div class="jumbotron">
	  <h1 class="display-4">Night 1</h1>
	  <p class="lead">Nighttime is when the action begins. Take action now if you have the role of werewolf, minion, seer or robber.</p>
	  <hr class="my-4">
	  <p>Action for werewolves and minion: Secretly see who the werewolves are so you can work with your wolf team on day 2.</p>
	  <p>Action for Seer: Choose one player's role to check.</p>
	  <p>Action for Robber: Choose one player's role to rob. When you rob someone's role, you will swap your roles on day 2. Example: If you rob a werewolf, you will be in the wolf team on day 2.</p>
	  <p>Go to morning when everyone has finished taking action. </p>
	  <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="/day2" role="button">Go to morning</a>
	</div>

	<div class="container">
	  <div class="row">
	  <% players.forEach(function(player){ %>
		  <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-3">	
			<div class="card">
			  <div class="card-body">
				<h5 class="card-title"><%= player.name %> </h5>
				<a href="/action/<%= player._id %>" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Take action</a>
			  </div>
			</div>
		</div>
	  <% }); %>
	  </div>
	</div>


		
<%- include("./partials/footer") %>